</entry><entry><p>Post-Channel</p></entry><entry><p>Express Card/ M.2/ Add-In Card.</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="SECTION_118064E5-618B-4BF0-AE18-81080E9C2821"><title>Mainstream, Premium Mid Loss (PML), Rx,Tx</title><table id="TABLE_118064E5-618B-4BF0-AE18-81080E9C2821_1"><title>PCIe Gen 2 M.2 Topology Mainstream, Premium Mid Loss (PML), Rx,Tx Routing Guidelines</title><tgroup cols="4"><thead><row><entry>Segment</entry><entry>Tline Type</entry><entry>Max Length Segment (mm)</entry><entry>Max Length Segment Note</entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry><p>BO</p></entry><entry><p>DSL, MS, SL</p></entry><entry><p>15.2</p></entry><entry><p /></entry></row><row><entry><p>M1 + M2</p></entry><entry><p>DSL, MS, SL</p></entry><entry><p /></entry><entry><p>Max length is BO+M1+M2+M3 &lt; 229 mm</p></entry></row><row><entry><p>M3</p></entry><entry><p>MS</p></entry><entry><p>8</p></entry><entry><p /></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><p>Max Length Total (mm): 229</p><p>Max Length Total Note: Max length is BO+M1+M2+M3 &lt; 229 mm</p></section></body></topic>